text: The Medog eastern frog or Medog papilla-tongued frog (Liurana medogensis) is a frog. It lives in China and India. Scientists have seen it between 2700 and 3200 meters above sea level in China and between 851 and 2500 meters above sea level in India. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia
title: Liurana medogensis
